      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable showroom condition, this vehicle represents the zenith of automotive preservation. Every detail, from the lustrous exterior finish to the untouched interior upholstery, underscores a history of meticulous stewardship and climate-controlled storage. Mechanically indistinguishable from new, this offering provides an unrivaled opportunity for the sophisticated buyer to acquire a specimen of true investment grade. We invite rigorous inspection to confirm its flawless integrity.",
