    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a breathtaking, collector-grade example that has been preserved in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior is truly flawless, featuring a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings. Every panel gap is factory-perfect. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather bolsters show no signs of entry wear, and the original protective plastics remain on several trim pieces. All electronics, from the high-fidelity sound system to the responsive infotainment, function exactly as they did on day one. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history and an engine bay so clean it looks untouched. This car drives with the tight, quiet precision of a brand-new vehicle, offering a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to own a showroom-standard masterpiece.",
      "price": 44900.0,
